sourcesContent: function r(e){var t,f,n="";if("string"==typeof e||"number"==typeof e)n+=e;else if("object"==typeof e)if(Array.isArray(e))for(t=0;t<e.length;t++)e[t]&&(f=r(e[t]))&&(n&&(n+=" "),n+=f);else for(t in e)e[t]&&(n&&(n+=" "),n+=t);return n}export default function(...e){for(var t,f,n=0,o="";n<e.length;)(t=e[n++])&&(f=r(t))&&(o&&(o+=" "),o+=f);return o}
